Tower, our logs show you are missing an additional nine fuel cells.

259
00:28:33,254 --> 00:28:34,255
你能确定吗
Can you confirm?

260
00:28:34,339 --> 00:28:36,466
不 指挥中心 应该是10块
Negative, Mission, that number is 10.

261
