00:31:23,299 --> 00:31:25,051
这是一个方位坐标
It's a set of coordinates.

282
00:31:25,677 --> 00:31:27,262
指向17号区域
Grid 17.

283
00:31:27,512 --> 00:31:29,389
是归航信标
It's a goddamn homing beacon.

284
00:31:29,556 --> 00:31:30,765
17号区域
Grid 17.

285
00:31:31,182 --> 00:31:32,350
那儿有什么东西
What the hell is out there?

286
00:31:36,020 --> 00:31:38,189
没什么 荒山野岭的
Nothing. It's the middle of nowhere.

287
00:31:39,190 --> 00:31:41,109
到底怎么回事
What is going on?

288
00:31:41,276 --> 00:31:45,405
他们发射地球外信号的目的是什么 杰克
Why would the scavs send a signal off-planet, Jack?

289
00:31:47,115 --> 00:31:48,658
我去关掉它
I'm shutting it down.

290
00:32:01,504 --> 00:32:04,465
49号 你改变了航向 正飞往安全区边界
Tech-49, check your course. You're headed right for the border.

291
00:32:05,758 --> 00:32:09,137
你将有遭到核辐射的可能
That radiation will cook you from the inside before you know it.

292
00:32:09,304 --> 00:32:11,264
好吧 维多利亚 我看到它了
It's okay, Vika. I see it.

293
00:32:13,725 --> 00:32:18,208
