I may go off-comm.

295
00:32:21,399 --> 00:32:22,567
杰克 我们必须保持联系 
Jack, we should keep in contact.

296
00:32:22,692 --> 00:32:23,901
让我知道你在哪儿
Just let me know where you are.

297
00:32:25,445 --> 00:32:27,071
你听见了吗
Do you COPY?

