Jack, the Tet's offline. (STAMMERING) I don't have control.

355
00:38:55,918 --> 00:38:57,044
停止射击
Stand down!

356
00:39:04,593 --> 00:39:07,638
杰克・哈珀 49号
Jack Harper, Tech-49.

