00:41:12,596 --> 00:41:14,181
无人机屠杀我们的同胞
drones killed the crew from one of our own ships.

366
00:41:14,640 --> 00:41:16,058
看看长官有什么杨的反应
See what Command makes of that.

367
00:41:18,185 --> 00:41:19,395
(GASPS)

